<scriptment id="62000" point="spielberg" localizationstatus="original" fictionaldate="2011-09-07" status="final">
	<part>
		<narration>Yuki is watching a video of the Electronic Entertainment Expo in 2011. A man is on a podium.</narration>
		<line id="1000" speaker="spielberg" voicelang="en">My apologies to the video game community.</line>
		<line id="2000" speaker="spielberg" voicelang="en">Recently, my film projects have been occupying much of my time.</line>
		<line id="3000" speaker="spielberg" voicelang="en">Deal with your business or it will deal with you, they say, so &#x2014;</line>
		<line id="4000" speaker="spielberg" voicelang="en">I've decided to turn my full attention to film.</line>
	</part>
</scriptment>